<div id="review_1726649732" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1726649732" />
    <a title="Devlin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1193735-devlin"><img alt="Devlin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1221263029p2/1193735.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1726649732?book_show_action=true">Oct 29, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Devlin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Devlin" href="/user/show/1193735-devlin">Devlin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780553575491" href="/book/show/359390.Holy_Fire">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1726649732" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11505472624443892199">Interesting ideas but no cohesive plot development to sustain interest. Sometimes the writing can be melodramatic; it needs a good solid edit. But the ideas of what it means to live forever, our relation to technology and medicine and Sterling&apos;s abundant imagination and vision of a our future are wonderful. </span>
  <span id="freeText11505472624443892199" style="display:none">Interesting ideas but no cohesive plot development to sustain interest. Sometimes the writing can be melodramatic; it needs a good solid edit. But the ideas of what it means to live forever, our relation to technology and medicine and Sterling's abundant imagination and vision of a our future are wonderful. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11505472624443892199" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


