        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1114407075" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12204911251167529565">A 94 yr old minor gerontocrat receives an experimental rejuvenation treatment that sets her off on a Gulliverian ramble through western civ in 2090. Entertaining, thoughtful, prescient. More full of ideas than action.</span>

